Mediawiki-Spider version 0.3
=============================

This is designed for two main things: copying wikis to flat HTML files in much the same manner as a wget might do it, and creating sites that contain the content of more than one wiki in static HTML. 

Mediawiki::Spider is still in active development.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  HTML::Extract

